Support, seems like an easy mod to please many users. Not everyone burns by points. you all used to have a burndown by hour chart. Please bring it back. I imagine this would be super easy, just copy the gadget and use remaining time (in hours) rater than story points.

Best practices aside if a user wants to view a burn-down by hours (and there are quite a few of us,  just google it) why not provide this ability so users don't have to seek some labor intensive work around. Does not help my brand loyalty.

